
# SRO Investigation Lifecycle Architecture

## System Integration Epics & User Stories

**Document Version:** 1.0  
**Status:** Target State Design Phase  
**Scope:** ESYS ↔ Salesforce ↔ Portal ↔ Comms System ↔ TRIM integrations

