## Success Criteria & Rollout

**Go-Live Readiness:**

- All Phase 1–4 epics complete + tested
- API health monitoring: >99% success rate across all integrations
- SLA tracking: all gates (T+0, T+5, T+7, T+10, PW-005, 60d) automated + monitored
