**Rollout Strategy:**

- Parallel run: ESYS/SF both active for 2 weeks (manual PIC duplication, compare results)
- Cutover: disable PIC creation directly in SF; all new PICs via ESYS API only
- Monitoring: daily integration health reports first month; weekly thereafter
- Support: dedicated integration support contact (24h response SLA for P1 API failures)

